See https://github.com/google/ExoPlayer/tree/release-v2/extensions/ffmpeg

1.
build command:

./build_ffmpeg.sh "$(pwd)/extensions/ffmpeg/src/main" "<NDK_PATH>" "linux-x86_64" "pcm_mulaw" "pcm_alaw"


2.
Download NDK version: NDK r21

3.
HOST_PLATFORM = "linux-x86_64"
use "darwin-x86_64" for Mac OS X

4.
FFMPEG version: 4.2
git checkout release/4.2

5.
create a symbolic link "ffmpeg" to the path of downloaded FFMPEG

6.
enable decoder: pcm_mulaw and pcm_alaw